{
  "stem": "18056.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 473.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how we arrived in America on-- in-- in January 1947, the 16th of January.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "New York.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, we came into New York.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was very interesting and all these big buildings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And for us, it was fantastic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my wife, she was-- Ursula was a little more-- she was more intelligent.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had more education.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She-- she knew some English.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So yeah, it was better for her than for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For me, it was very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In New York?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, 153rd Street in Manhattan.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was the-- the-- a Jewish organization.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, all the refugees, as they come to-- came to the United States, the churches, the synagogues, the-- all kinds of organizations would help.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Me, being Jewish, it was, of course, the-- the-- they took care of me, the-- for new Americans, and they helped us out with the first, I think, $50.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We got $200 or whatever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that money, with that money we were able to buy the first apartment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we are not religious people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we are-- we-- we believe in being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we don't believe necessarily about, you know, all the religious part of the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we went to synagogue once in a while, yes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to a-- they had set up in New York-- there were the schools set up for the refugees.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a-- a school that I went to, I think, 20 times and 20 lessons.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's how I learned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And above all, I learned is in the movies, because you learn a lot because there were two features, and it was like a three-hour movie deal.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went at least once a week.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After applying to become a-- a US citizen.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
